  m_text: "We have initiated your transfer.Please check your account for receipt.\nProcessing
    the transaction will take at least 2 business days.\n\nYou can how initiate more
    transactions at other tiers. Generally,higher \namounts are processed faster.\nAdditionally,
    the more transaction requests you have from a single \naccount, the  quicker
    the processing speed wwill be. Please note thatall your pending transaction requests
    will be settled simultaneously once the \nwaiting period concludes."
